@startuml reservation_diagram
title Резервирование товара

actor "Клиентское приложение" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Сервис резервирования" as ReservationService
database "Распределенный кеш" as Cache
database "Хранилище резервов" as ReservationStore
database "Хранилище событий" as EventStore
queue "Event Bus" as EventBus

Client -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/reservations\nREST/HTTPS\nIdempotency-Key
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Gateway: Проверка токена доступа,\nпроверка прав,\nограничение частоты запросов

Gateway -> ReservationService: CreateReservation(skuId, storeId, qty, userId)\nREST или gRPC / HTTP/2\nIdempotency-Key
activate ReservationService

ReservationService -> ReservationStore: Проверка Idempotency-Key
activate ReservationStore

alt Повторный запрос с тем же Idempotency-Key
    ReservationStore --> ReservationService: Ранее созданный результат
    deactivate ReservationStore

    ReservationService --> Gateway: 200 OK\nРезультат ранее выполненного резервирования
    deactivate ReservationService

    Gateway --> Client: 200 OK\nРезерв уже создан
    deactivate Gateway

else Новый запрос
    ReservationStore --> ReservationService: Запрос ранее не выполнялся
    deactivate ReservationStore

    ReservationService -> Cache: Захват распределенной блокировки\nпо skuId + storeId
    activate Cache

    alt Блокировка не получена
        Cache --> ReservationService: lock rejected
        deactivate Cache

        ReservationService --> Gateway: 409 Conflict\nРезервирование временно недоступно
        deactivate ReservationService

        Gateway --> Client: 409 Conflict\nПовторить позже
        deactivate Gateway

    else Блокировка получена
        Cache --> ReservationService: lock acquired
        deactivate Cache

        ReservationService -> Cache: Чтение доступного остатка\navailability:{skuId}:{storeId}
        activate Cache
        Cache --> ReservationService: available_qty,\nreserved_qty,\nupdated_at
        deactivate Cache

        alt Доступного остатка недостаточно
            ReservationService -> Cache: Освобождение блокировки
            activate Cache
            Cache --> ReservationService: OK
            deactivate Cache

            ReservationService --> Gateway: 409 Conflict\nНедостаточно товара для резерва
            deactivate ReservationService

            Gateway --> Client: 409 Conflict\nТовар недоступен для резервирования
            deactivate Gateway

        else Доступный остаток достаточен
            ReservationService -> ReservationStore: INSERT reservation\nstatus = ACTIVE,\nexpires_at,\nIdempotency-Key
            activate ReservationStore
            ReservationStore --> ReservationService: reservationId
            deactivate ReservationStore

            ReservationService -> EventStore: APPEND ReservationCreated
            activate EventStore
            EventStore --> ReservationService: eventId
            deactivate EventStore

            ReservationService -> EventBus: Publish ReservationCreated
            activate EventBus
            EventBus --> ReservationService: ack
            deactivate EventBus

            ReservationService -> Cache: Обновление счетчиков резерва\nи освобождение блокировки
            activate Cache
            Cache --> ReservationService: OK
            deactivate Cache

            ReservationService --> Gateway: 201 Created\nreservationId,\nexpires_at,\nstatus
            deactivate ReservationService

            Gateway --> Client: 201 Created\nРезерв создан
            deactivate Gateway
        end
    end
end

@enduml